{"h1ff16d2eg21d7g4031g868agee5a6af3476e": ["Miri... MIRI!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "fa2eb1f7-1e16-142f-a4dc-da7be8cb3334"], "hb5651871gba0bg48d9g9f4age82b2eb6a6aa": ["Miri? Who are you looking for?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "a5bdd6ee-83aa-aaeb-716d-50749154cc86"], "h0e013de0g7926g4a20g83efgb96ba336576e": ["My wife. She was outside when the goblins came.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "59c46777-28c7-5e3f-a123-b29146c86abb"], "h0a5d0bc6g4885g4cd8gbfaeg6bd5f9d88943": ["She was wearing a green blouse. Brown hair, about this tall.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "ffe6d4c8-446e-f5a7-dc3a-667437cdfff5"], "hc3f431cfgbe9bg400bgbcabg8ea9b784e000": ["Have you seen her?", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "5f52fd94-b1d7-f778-bab2-d33c3d73515a"], "h422f4ba7g0e47g4a0eg894agdab984de4a9a": ["Sorry, I haven't. But I can look for her.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "bac94877-058f-94e7-6b2d-6bc1c3e69721"], "h53ebfadfg3a77g40dbg826eg4b01fbfa0b07": ["Thank you. She can't have gone far.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "06c1b310-572f-ca6c-b213-b523ae2ce2b5"], "h3ce924f4g9113g4f6dg8a26ga00530ca43fb": ["She's almost certainly dead.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "ce7467c2-2d57-c301-f413-44eeb519b275"], "h6abe7eadg7fadg4454g9751g2e902dfd461c": ["I found her body.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "46ba9323-a9ac-7766-e444-28418f8426f5"], "h8f7289f9gd30fg439ag87e5g516a2eaf5e4d": ["No. No, it can't be. I need to see.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "f455a80c-a22b-7349-0f31-c359fdba1a27"], "h9dc8b1cbg9b2fg435cga484g38670a063451": ["Save your breath. There aren't any survivors.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "b461bcdd-1a57-8455-f59e-1782c3cdead9"], "hebca09adg3dbdg4a1eg8ca7g201cc30d961e": ["You don't know that!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "26f5c28e-a01b-8f49-b079-b37aaef1c977"], "h3ec2b11bg0a8fg4054gb6cdgacd006fe8961": ["MIRI!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "8a9e631b-6d5a-0900-c24c-d35fca896c9b"], "h2d1c7191g35e7g4308ga76egdb311b55a46e": ["She's dead. I found her body in one of the burned buildings.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "681387e4-8487-cabb-0a49-0367d645fdcd"], "h29cb6069g66a5g4722g978dg5d8f36c8dfa3": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "37b72a17-1460-5773-a190-1bfcfff1390d"], "hd1de5b36gdc25g4edaga108g6db5ce046ead": ["Have you found my Miri?", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "1ffcc7b7-8035-aee5-c3c4-d26bc7ffe1fd"], "h41b5dca9gdfc1g4f02gad41gbd2fd8eb7d2b": ["Can you tell me what she looks like?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "3f7ada09-1496-a89a-a360-0aacdcb049ab"], "h4347e921g438fg46bcga4fbg2308834790e3": ["No, I haven't.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "6d321c85-5dae-a592-3a83-9098ae29a4d9"], "h873673c4g40d8g44fagb171g0332df3de9d3": ["I have to keep looking. Miri!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "8e5c99e1-ceea-5b9d-1cd4-1c8216918f66"], "ha576a2fege919g4c07g92dfgdcabd8a23e7e": ["I won't forget what you did for me. For <i>her</i>. Thank you.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "e5a7b404-21cd-bf39-95bc-b291f2d39013"], "hbb386333ge3b8g4821gacefg5260eaeadc56": ["Leave us alone.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "cf8f515a-5ee7-574e-2281-fa2241c962d6"], "h662ece2dge574g4486gaf52g303cc174cb18": ["Miri, no... gods, no, no, no!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "8291421c-4b11-51ab-8ba5-53b15c3af056"], "h3b9f4c71g9806g41f5g85aag6f7066f75521": ["You should've stayed... you should've been with me.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "f2dae74e-856d-13d8-bb6c-a4ac9356c012"], "hd0a6fc2ag8936g48dfgadd8g95cff8ce784c": ["How did you two get separated?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "963529dd-8673-3c1e-a5a0-4a54b63ee47c"], "h3ac9df34g8c2eg44a9g89d9g5c64e5c43391": ["I was in our room. We had a fight.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "53d89a85-b19f-9073-ac44-1a2622f8ee6e"], "h2f338441g2e7cg41f6gb6acgd2a89c64a054": ["If I'd just kept my mouth shut about that bloody dowry, she'd... she'd still be here.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "65ee180e-db1e-ca75-45fb-5edbda411263"], "hfee16ab9g813fg45e1g97f3g94006fc14172": ["About that dowry - pretty sure I found it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "709eada4-8faa-8ed0-6c3c-992036c3b7be"], "h7989f4b9gde01g4fa6g8e61g08b4ab73815d": ["You did? Please - she'd want her sister to have it.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "809ac048-eef0-4e77-c08e-95bd219ab92a"], "h0038c6bdg9531g44dfg95aag17ef6c0d2d2b": ["Here. Take it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "0c322ebd-dd84-5aea-acf5-c7060bf3c3ec"], "hf1e1a9efg8c78g4e51g9839g0f9f9288eb10": ["Maybe I judged you too quickly. Thank you.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "34d454b2-da9a-f483-a440-93d1d10098ce"], "h40deb888g2b90g42d7gb5b1g4bb617ae8f2a": ["I'd need some time alone with her... to say goodbye.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "b83531be-151e-43e8-5070-28271345dd08"], "h309f4677gc9deg4ec5g8b6dgf20b09e0bf6d": ["I know this doesn't change anything, but it helps. Thank you.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "b955a734-3448-257b-b53e-3c967e26138c"], "hab5c3ac2g2df6g490bgb51egdb4dd0338d3e": ["I'm keeping it. Consider it payment for saving your life.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "705eea45-541d-5ff3-9a75-87e6e0b84e2a"], "h4c47321eg9c35g47c9g92f5g129412d4615d": ["You... what?", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "c2930af4-b945-3c2e-1f86-65c969546d80"], "hbf4f6967gcd8ag41f4g81abgd486060a60d5": ["Fine. I hope you choke on it.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "b3f17dc0-034a-6c9d-cce3-c10e2b818128"], "hd1b4baaag381dg4de6gb6a7g67a0ccc63375": ["What's a few coins? The sister won't miss them.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "8ce51863-6470-0219-5e3e-e2926d51c856"], "h97427b51gdbcfg4a8eg8f4ag184fa5834253": ["Allow me to apologise on Lae'zel's behalf, sir. Her lack of tact is a burden to us all.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "2be1b5e4-cbb2-f9f0-bb2e-d66bccb36683"], "ha797e38ega63ag4ee8g944fgc320510a776b": ["Allow me to apologise on Shadowheart's behalf, sir. Her lack of tact is a burden to us all.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "fc26b0ae-6918-6738-518f-face1436cdc8"], "hc38605dbg031eg4309ga0c0gc06c5f178335": ["Allow me to apologise on Astarion's behalf, sir. His lack of tact is a burden to us all.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "4c77b299-2f94-1b6f-c728-ae439b2281ed"], "h9439b4f8g8a27g45f8g9791gd14fbd76a053": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "d7c1afbb-85e9-05ca-1d37-2946e4dc01ed"], "h37f2241dg6229g49d9gb99ag75c0f22e2f18": ["|KARLACH: How could you say that?! The man is mourning!|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "c64802fd-0719-94d8-de44-d3ab0e2f8244"], "h944a409eg1f69g497cga8feg130e96c9188a": ["_", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "9921e5f4-60d1-b344-5849-27d1f0271734"], "h0fb7dc41g193eg42ddg8477gb4d88b2b6b6f": ["I'm <i>overwhelmed</i> by your selflessness.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "f99fc6f7-2943-3c80-3b99-15c6210c1979"], "h2a71c799g838cg4f9ag8a29g113792b04ebb": ["He can afford it - he's got one less mouth to feed now.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "ede2246d-4982-207a-ad82-79ea314371e4"], "h6cdd118bg6e0cg4a7cg8645g7e3f28435ca7": ["You took the gold? I was rather hoping for the body...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "77cd2f7a-b936-6df0-b4bb-c49099c10cf5"], "h39f2459ag9d81g4fafg88e0g898a48da96ff": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "0e576f60-7448-2089-a400-78eafb620234"], "h8cfe3a3bg59dcg4886gbaeeg59422a56c954": ["_", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "2acad1e8-006e-a034-5f23-6574b5b8e95a"], "h8646abd2ge7e4g43f7g9f96g8962a4c976ae": ["By the hells' fires, has your heart shrunk so small?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "6b29fd48-978d-0d6b-7709-0ab49617e40f"], "hc6b18ef0g9c5ag4607g96dfg759ebd738d38": ["That was a rather unimpressive display of pettiness if you ask me.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "755b9ec9-df74-d6dd-b7fa-99ff1e5f87dc"], "h4d032a22g1aacg4a48ga926g33c336a57676": ["|KARLACH: What the hell is wrong with you?!|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "bfafd57b-5b4e-ea7b-a7b6-ac61d5472617"], "hb6886b79ga4d3g4c97gb0ceg4ab9deddfeaf": ["Just go. Please.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "02e39303-2341-eeb4-4728-825686d8ba49"], "hb4981742g7326g4f97gb034ge1b1af6684ad": ["Sorry, but I don't have it anymore.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "be205ce9-3d8d-90a5-0b12-edf06f2d8fbb"], "h121ce5e6ga51eg47beg9ad4g3a426859ddb2": ["Then get it back! I'm sorry, it's just... it's important.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "e3b33a15-6d25-734b-a3c9-21c23221fa02"], "hfe969b60gfb50g4f9bg8bc9g5e20ec09eba7": ["Please, it'd mean so much to her. ", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "44c6f4c4-8db8-4797-995f-8c1f6a56bc58"], "h24363384g3950g4c72g8075ga12850b77e63": ["About that dowry - I know where it is.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "95bff8b9-2ac3-5ca8-45a1-8b77e48037cc"], "h799520ecgc90ag474bga423g0b35a27724c5": ["You do? Please, can you return it to me? She'd want her sister to have it.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "6cf33bcf-63e5-a75a-8bce-bd7285ca85c8"], "h35aaa2d9g2383g491bg9e9bgbf2f370b2918": ["What was that about a dowry?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "0f1100af-57be-a078-ab62-edefccd05609"], "h3a391b7cg3541g4bdegb3f9gfb5d7866d973": ["It's for her sister's wedding. I made a stupid joke about keeping it.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "be58795c-6eaa-261d-d91d-45798da48b95"], "h3bcb4d98gf965g48bbg8ae5g7802ee81ba0a": ["We argued about it for hours. Then she took the dowry and left.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "a2f07578-283d-ad95-fbf4-6ccc7b246ffa"], "hd7fb0c02g46f4g4437g913dg3e8485da92cf": ["She said I'd never see her again. She was right.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "53671b0f-0e8a-eb7b-521a-84d78fdab069"], "h542e6e1agefd8g4cb8ga91bg5531ae6a7f2e": ["I think I found the dowry.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "b1bbfa0b-c06f-6c66-6b4e-f65f07358512"], "hb9d90654g820dg4880gb9bbg99fb1ff6f81d": ["This isn't on you. There was no way you could have known.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "26c3e0c6-a7df-7b0a-e2f9-2a422b4b1d76"], "hd987ddd1g089ag4fc4ga7c2gc133c3934f21": ["I'm sorry, Miri. I'm so sorry.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "fffebf92-39a8-75cd-06cb-43bb9870e028"], "h7a0315c1g6817g4014g8458g13e41008d81d": ["Please, just go. I need a moment with her.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "40f564aa-c30b-3d76-7e5a-8be55be90c97"], "hbdac4913g4159g40d3g84d1g931e987f8280": ["Count your blessings. At least you're still alive.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "46eec6a4-1d4b-93f5-8ec9-ce03dc2bbe0c"], "h6bb3e4a2ga0eeg4396g96ddg16d9103a579f": ["How is this a blessing?", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "906a8ca9-f5fa-8980-7b43-96f2c395cabf"], "ha799bddag8955g42c8gb331g9ea9a936772f": ["You should've let me burn.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "e90da42d-d565-790a-bcd0-293af1c247d2"], "hbb439556g1f01g45e1gb60bgf9e1466fea53": ["She was trying to get back to you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "3282aa38-707c-36df-f062-bc63b42f64fd"], "he8a42b32g8e4cg4534gaabfg7d8f233eeedf": ["No. No! Why didn't you run? Why didn't you hide?", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "c23c8039-6791-0069-afba-72ac0afb0313"], "h2da1ea10g9dd0g45fegb4bbg38c4172a8a83": ["This is all my fault. We were arguing. She ran off.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "e407e6c6-6772-d177-521f-29cc4d0b3806"], "hb9bd64bfg9a5eg4cc4gae37g2ba55ee94e1d": ["It wouldn't have made a difference.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "53285c3c-c1c0-f20c-80f5-806d6eddf1eb"], "h0947be8bg21bfg4352gad9eg6dd9fcbec0d7": ["She would've survived! If only I'd kept my mouth shut about that bloody dowry...", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "bcd61020-b081-a36f-509b-b7242a50e02b"], "hb345a860g65b1g40f5g9e3bg544f617b5d91": ["What am I going to do? She's all I had.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "1ceb4321-b5a3-d55b-7ed4-ceba865305c2"], "h2cf40538gdc40g4492g901cg0a1c4e7cd055": ["You'll be all right, with time.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "89fed933-4987-6cda-8a14-cf75bc3bd1c9"], "h20751f9fg3a2dg4a04g9a6dge4d96902f518": ["This will never be right.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "09ba381b-32cb-44d6-2fb1-9ee77123c60d"], "h17abd723g2df1g4e48ga124g57972a213c66": ["I can pray for her, if you like.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "11e7b31f-2e18-83c9-2475-45d11f9ff68e"], "h9bd2e091gf1f9g4d52gb557ge8c79d4eb0b3": ["She follows - <i>followed</i>  Gond.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "ca4a60af-52fa-dc93-47f9-3e9b3cd7bd61"], "h55b8ee7cge6e0g4e4dgb33ag6b0d0bebf7ec": ["I pray to thee, Gond - guide Miri to peace in death.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "a34a053f-12e1-524b-be8a-b1e575089136"], "h87d3fa7fg1707g45e3g846fga1d42d0c80cd": ["Thank you. She would've like that.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "dfbdd607-5c02-566d-7172-75b11c3d53a8"], "h9b9ee904ga427g4ebagba71g49c613e93b4a": ["The gods won't listen to me. It's my fault she's dead.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "d875356e-c246-fa77-9fc3-7b092e98df82"], "hbe15c45ag5d51g4855ga0degbb151d491467": ["<i>Pray to your own god instead.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "1f919b6f-e157-4a98-c95f-dba1d3335ea8"], "h153e37abg0f76g4729gbe4egd373220011d1": ["That's... thank you. I hope your god listens.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "9fc5313f-1e3b-8fce-e75b-4b275933d93d"], "h9d29e641g474fg48f4gace2ge275acaebd07": ["There is no Gond.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "e93fe090-7e34-09bf-338e-5c9e6e38a5ac"], "h6b5736f0g5534g419bgb600gea51faef8058": ["Her body's not even cold and you're questioning her faith? ", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "4d717166-e907-5f20-66a0-ab093dba33c7"], "h8421ea33gd006g4833gac09g81b739c4fc59": ["Go to hell.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "1c8b39a2-e3ac-c086-a9c3-71294dc9e65d"], "hb1c9c58cg8671g47c2g8b0bg1ca885279a55": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "a69036a2-ca6b-f9dd-1450-f94d9ea01acb"], "hcd40ebefg9b32g4482g9e0dgdaeca12999d8": ["*Sob.*", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "e1a30499-4948-be54-a24d-afef3a1547c1"], "he5104b3dg237fg47d1gb10dg01dd7a016e48": ["Didn't you say something about a dowry?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "2d012676-6a7c-22c7-8cc7-088f1c9fcaf2"], "he18245aaga686g4c40g8160g20120ebc484c": ["I found the dowry. Here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "4b0e341f-5f34-eef6-85d9-cc52894bad97"], "h97a49ae2g70d2g4c52g9d28ge5e000649bee": ["I found this chest - I think it's yours.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "e78b05be-e12f-321b-1179-d29f59b6990d"], "hb818fa5dg5c39g4d94g9301g0d6b93c16a13": ["That dowry? I'm keeping it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "0287ddf4-53b1-52c3-eb93-4f9e8bc95913"], "hcb44c319g77a8g43d0g989ege05d048a811e": ["That dowry? I'm keeping it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_StuckHalfElf_Freed.html", "0ead2cbc-fa38-0732-0050-6ce44d4b742e"]}